## ğŸ§± Network Security

### ğŸ”¹ Network ACL (NACL)
- Works at **subnet level**
- Stateless
- Controls inbound & outbound traffic

### ğŸ”¹ Security Groups
- Works at **instance level**
- Stateful
- Acts like a firewall for EC2

ğŸ“Œ **Rule of Thumb**:
> NACL = Subnet gatekeeper  
> Security Group = Instance bodyguard ğŸ›¡ï¸

